={1\over n!}{(-1)^{n-1}\over2^n}1\cdot3\cdots(2n-3)\frac{2\cdot4\cdot6...(2n-4)}{2^{n-2}(n-2)!}=
={1\over n!}{(-1)^{n-1}\over2^{2n-2}}\frac{(2n-3)!}{(n-2)!}\frac{(2n-2)(2n-1)2n}{(n-1)n\cdot2^2\cdot(2n-1)}=
